import React from 'react';
import { Card, CardContent, Typography, Grid } from '@mui/material';

const Testimonials = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container spacing={3}  margin={10} >
      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: 'rgb(129, 82, 210)', color: 'white', borderRadius: 4, p: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="subtitle2" fontWeight="bold">
              Daniel Clifford
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="caption">Verified Graduate</Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              I received a job offer mid-course, and the subjects I learned were current, if not more so, in the company I joined. I honestly feel I got every pennyâ€™s worth.
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              I was an EMT for many years before I joined the bootcamp...
            </Typography>

          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>

      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: 'rgb(94, 106, 127)', color: 'white', borderRadius: 4, p: 2, boxShadow: 3 }}>
          <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="subtitle2" fontWeight="bold">
              Jonathan Walters
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="caption">Verified Graduate</Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              The team was very supportive and kept me motivated
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              I started as a total newbie with virtually no coding skills...
            </Typography>
          
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
      

      <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
        <Card sx={{ backgroundColor: '#F3F4F6', color: 'Black', borderRadius: 4, p: 2, boxShadow: 3, height:800 }}>
          <CardContent>
          <Typography variant="subtitle2" fontWeight="bold">
              Kira Whittle
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="caption">Verified Graduate</Typography>
            <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight="bold" gutterBottom>
              Such a life-changing experience. Highly recommended!
            </Typography>
            <Typography variant="body2" gutterBottom>
              Before joining the bootcamp, I have never written a line of code...
            </Typography>
           
          </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>

      
    </Grid>
  );
};

export default Testimonials;
